title: Short trip up Rollins Pass
header: Cameron and I attempted this road back in May but it was still burried in several feet of snow.  Today I got revenge.
images: Panorama photo looking South towards Tolland Road
While I was taking the panorama someone stopped and offered to take my picture.  There were alot of other motorcycles and cars up there that day.
This is the start of the trail.  Muddy but no snow today.
